[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1226511","time":"2017-4-4 20:50","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"(✨️VIP 8✨️)","message":"<a href=\"/user/explorare\" class=\"l\">@Explorare</a> 求助…","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1226512","time":"2017-4-4 20:54","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"不是某些字体用假字重么？写个 CSS 用同样方式加粗字体？<br><div class=\"codeHighlight\"><pre>font-weight: 100, 200, 300, 400, 500, 600, 700, 800, 900;</pre></div>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-2","id":"1226516","time":"2017-4-4 21:00","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"字体混搭是挺容易出现这个问题的，比如同样字号、字重的 MS YaHei 和 Calibri 实际尺寸就不一样，没法简单的混搭。然而实际上 YaHei 的英文部分就是 Calibri，调整了尺寸和字重。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-3","id":"1226518","time":"2017-4-4 21:05","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: 不是某些字体用假字重么？写个 CSS 用同样方式加粗字体？<br>font-weight: 100, 200, 300, 400, 500, 600, 700, 800, 900;</q></div>啥？CSS不能凭空变出不存在的字重。不会因为你写了900就给你加到最粗的，只会选粗体。Meiryo UI粗体又相对过粗，而且没有粗体的粗体。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-4","id":"1226519","time":"2017-4-4 21:09","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: Explorare 说: 不是某些字体用假字重么？写个 CSS 用同样方式加粗字体？<br>font-weight: 100, 200, 300, 400, 500, 600, 700, 800, 900;...</q></div>确实。另外你不觉得英文部分的字重相对中文部分粗么？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-5","id":"1226522","time":"2017-4-4 21:16","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: 确实。另外你不觉得英文部分的字重相对中文部分粗么？</q></div>看得出来，实际上一般中文字体自带的英文总是比中文笔画略粗一点，因为中文更密。这个还可以接受。<br>但相比中文疏的假名不应该比中文更细。有没有跟Meiryo UI差不多性质的日文字体？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-6","id":"1226526","time":"2017-4-4 21:47","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: Explorare 说: 确实。另外你不觉得英文部分的字重相对中文部分粗么？看得出来，实际上一般中文字体自带的英文总是比中文笔画略粗一点，因为中文更密。这个还可以接受。<br>但相比中文疏的假名不应该比中文...</q></div><a href=\"https://www.fonts.com/font/microsoft-corporation/ms-gothic/proportional\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">MS Gothic Proportional (MS PGothic)</a><br><a href=\"https://www.fonts.com/font/microsoft-corporation/ms-mincho/proportional\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">MS Mincho Proportional (MS PMincho)</a><br><a href=\"https://www.fonts.com/font/microsoft-corporation/mingliu/proportional\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">MS MingLiU Proportional</a><br>Osaka<br>平成明朝<br>モナーフォント<br>IPA Pフォント"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-7","id":"1226527","time":"2017-4-4 22:00","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: MS Gothic Proportional (MS PGothic)<br>MS Mincho Proportional (MS PMincho)<br>MS MingLiU Proportional<br>Osak...</q></div>呃…好像都挺旧的？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-8","id":"1226528","time":"2017-4-4 22:02","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: Explorare 说: MS Gothic Proportional (MS PGothic)<br>MS Mincho Proportional (MS PMincho)<br>MS MingLiU Prop...</q></div>是啊，就 Meiryo UI 是比较新的。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-9","id":"1226534","time":"2017-4-4 22:21","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: 是啊，就 Meiryo UI 是比较新的。</q></div>我查了下“Adobe Clean Han”这个字体，就是<a href=\"http://www.adobe.com/jp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">Adobe日文官网</a>用的字体…<br><a href=\"http://blogs.adobe.com/CCJKType/2016/10/a-new-face-for-adobe-redux.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">A New Face For Adobe—Redux</a><br>——用火狐那个查看器的字体测试，也是等宽的。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-10","id":"1226535","time":"2017-4-4 22:24","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<a href=\"http://www.monotype.com/fonts/tazugane/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">Tazugane™ Gothic</a>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-11","id":"1226542","time":"2017-4-4 23:00","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: Tazugane™ Gothic</q></div>src:url(\"<a href=\"https://fast.fonts.net/dv2/14/34472661-66c4-4d0c-bf11-fa5004d31026.woff2?d44f19a684109620e484157ba790e81816499089734fbd8e6abfc352469fbcd9cb812f3be187fae8936cdd8a6d5ef13de0c889367c5f695398befba20c15b7ec4758291bb59d3ca2ccd35330ef235b74ad2eece7bd419ad5ead21527a3a0454eed9d35db530bc72952a0dc8023076e93e7bbb09cdb0366b6&projectId=8e179764-093f-46a5-a5d4-0b813a1ad161\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://fast.fonts.net/dv2/14/34 ... 5-a5d4-0b813a1ad161</a>\") format('woff2');<br><br>成功了，火狐显示字体被调用了。但同时也失败了，这个字体是等宽的，奇怪的是同样字体链接在官网显示为不等宽，感觉像是用了我不懂的谜之技术把字偶距调整与字体分离了(?)。算了放弃，以后有空自己画个。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-12","id":"1226548","time":"2017-4-4 23:52","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: Explorare 说: Tazugane™ Gothicsrc:url(\"https://fast.fonts.net/dv2/14/34 ... 5-a5d4-0b813a1ad161\") for...</q></div><div class=\"codeHighlight\"><pre>font-feature-settings: \"palt\";</pre></div><br>这是 OpenType Font 的一个特性，理论上所有自带 palt 的 OpenType 字体都支持，比如 Source Han Sans 和 Source Han Serif。更多详见：<br><br><a href=\"https://helpx.adobe.com/typekit/using/open-type-syntax.html#palt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">Syntax for OpenType features in CSS</a><br><a href=\"https://helpx.adobe.com/jp/typekit/using/open-type-syntax.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">Typekitヘルプ | CSS での OpenType 機能の構文</a><br><a href=\"https://ics.media/entry/14087/3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">文字詰めできるCSSのfont-feature-settingsが凄い！ 日本語フォントこそ指定したい自動カーニング - ICS MEDIA</a>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-13","id":"1226549","time":"2017-4-5 00:10","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: 这是 OpenType Font 的一个特性<br>font-feature-settings: \"palt\"<br>Syntax for OpenType features in CSS<br>Typekitヘルプ ...</q></div>解决了，换成Source Han Sans。就是字型没有Meiryo UI活泼（总是不知足啊…）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-14","id":"1226550","time":"2017-4-5 00:17","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: 解决了，换成Source Han Sans。就是字型没有Meiryo UI活泼（总是不知足啊…）</q></div>那你就自己造个 medium 呗"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-15","id":"1226551","time":"2017-4-5 00:19","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: 那你就自己造个 medium 呗</q></div>等有时间吧。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-16","id":"1226727","time":"2017-4-6 00:45","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: font-feature-settings: \"palt\";<br>这是 OpenType Font 的一个特性，理论上所有自带 palt 的 OpenType 字体都支持，比如 Source Han Sa...</q></div>又冒出一个新问题：使用Source Han Sans会让/subject/*/characters、超展开 等页面上a.icons_cmt，a.tml_reply，a.cmt_reply（就是小气泡）抬高导致底下冒头。可能因为Source Han Sans的字符底下高一块。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-17","id":"1226728","time":"2017-4-6 00:52","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: Explorare 说: font-feature-settings: \"palt\";<br>这是 OpenType Font 的一个特性，理论上所有自带 palt 的 OpenType 字体都支持，比如 ...</q></div>来个截图"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-18","id":"1226805","time":"2017-4-6 12:27","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: 来个截图</q></div>也许样式写得不对，这是样式（节省长度去掉粗体斜体），你试试看能不能复现：<br><div class=\"codeHighlight\"><pre>@font-face {<br>font-family: jp;<br>src: local(\"Source Han Sans HW SC Regular\");<br>unicode-range:U+3040-30FF,U+2606;<br>font-feature-settings:\"palt\";<br>}<br>@font-face {<br>font-family: MSYH;<br>src: local(\"Microsoft YaHei UI\");<br>}<br>body {<br>font-family: jp,MSYH;<br>}</pre></div>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/62/76206.jpg","floor":"#2-19","id":"1226811","time":"2017-4-6 12:38","userId":"explorare","userName":"YJSNPI","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: Explorare 说: 来个截图也许样式写得不对，这是样式（节省长度去掉粗体斜体），你试试看能不能复现：<br>＠font-face {<br>font-family: jp;<br>src: local(\"Sour...</q></div>我不知道你那边的效果，给个截图看看。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2-20","id":"1226814","time":"2017-4-6 12:44","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Explorare</span> 说: 我不知道你那边的效果，给个截图看看。</q></div>等一下…话说这段写得没问题吗？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm